{
  "stem": "10587.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this is the same person that I describe where people-- you should tell me how they-- they say we need more people like this now to help the poor.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And your grandmother was such a terrific person that she made sure that the poor people had food and-- and were able to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You should take the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] help, you know, the service people-- the servants, and-- and help distribute foods and clothes and wood, and mainly a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My understanding is that the [GERMAN], [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the title was-- they were-- they were from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- her father, my grandmother's father, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was a professor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wrote a-- some special type of [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] books.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they always used to say how wonderful it was, you know, when-- because there was an expression that the Germans and the Austrians used to use.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe in those days they used to say, 'Leben und leben lassen.' Live and let live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this really was not-- I did not experience that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I experienced just the opposite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had very little to do with the non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we really didn't have any neighbors that would live next door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So all I know, that we know that-- we knew that the antisemitism was always present, especially on Easter time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to close the gate and put the [NON-ENGLISH] on the door, close the-- because they would throw stones.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Christmas was probably the worst time because they-- the Pollacks truly believed that the Jews killed Christ, they-- that the Jews killed their God.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the antisemitism in Poland was inbred in-- at-- in home already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When the chil-- they talked about it, about the dirty Jews at home before the children even started school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I do remember an incident where [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- where a group of children, when I was in school, they-- they were-- they was-- they were-- they got a hold of me and they-- I was hit with a stone in my head.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I came home all bloody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother almost fainted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But-- but I knew exactly which guy did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was maybe four or five of them together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, I'm not going to stand for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I-- I did seek this guy out separately.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it was a different situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he really-- he would not participate anymore because, one on one, they were not that brave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My teacher, I remember was a major in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all my-- all my siblings went to the same school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the parents' conference, they used to go and find out how-- and my-- I can't think of his name, but he would say, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It means, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bader, you should only have this much pleasure from the rest of your children, because [INAUDIBLE] is doing a terrific job.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, so-- I used to I used to work at it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- and my grandfather was-- when we-- when we used to get our report cards, he would-- I would get the biggest amount of the-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Someone would get maybe a dollar, maybe I would get $2 because they all knew that I would bring the best report card.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he would sit in the the main-- inside the square of our building, and the kids would pass by him, and he would reward them for-- for getting-- but he would give each one something, regardless.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I told him that I'm going to beat the hell out of him, and I did, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and since then, he would not participate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a radio towards the year-- I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was the end of-- before the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember having a radio.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we-- I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we also had, besides the radio, we had a micro-- a gramophone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to always, especially during the war where our parents would not-- didn't let the kids go out at night, so friends and relatives would come to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- and I would be given five pennies to keep it-- to-- I would crawl under the table and keep the gramophone-- I would wind it up constantly and replace-- and change the plates, the-- the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] record.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of-- because they danced and they-- so a lot of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] variety of music, I would say, a lot of the kind of music you can dance to.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
